ARE YOU WEARING?

17:56.743 --> 17:58.311
- NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.

17:58.345 --> 18:00.113
- WELL, MAKE SURE
THEY'RE NOT TOO TIGHT...

18:00.147 --> 18:01.848
'CAUSE TIGHTNESS
CONSTRICTS YOUR BALLS.

18:01.881 --> 18:03.450
