YOUR PAYLOAD.

18:15.162 --> 18:16.729
- YOU KNOW,
I THINK I'LL HIT THE GYM.

18:16.763 --> 18:18.465
VIC, DEBBIE, SEE YOU LATER.

18:18.498 --> 18:20.633
- BYE, HONEY.

18:20.667 --> 18:22.402
- LET ME OUT, SIS.

18:22.435 --> 18:24.671
- WHERE YOU GOING?

18:24.704 --> 18:28.641
- TO GET MICHAEL A PAIR OF MY
BIG, BAGGY FRUIT OF THE LOOMS.

18:34.447 --> 18:37.150
- BEN! YOU MIND
IF I WALK WITH YOU?

18:37.184 --> 18:39.786
- NO.
- ALL THAT BABY TALK.

18:39.819 --> 18:41.921
- I-I'M THRILLED FOR MICHAEL
AND THE GIRLS.

18:41.954 --> 18:43.823
- I NEVER WANTED KIDS,
MYSELF.

18:43.856 --> 18:46.526
- I DID. OF COURSE, THAT'S NOT
GOING TO HAPPEN NOW.

18:46.559 --> 18:48.528
- ONE OF THE WAYS WE'RE NOT
LIKE "THEM" ANYMORE.

18:48.561 --> 18:52.299
- I TRY NOT TO THINK ABOUT IT.
SOME DAYS, I EVEN SUCCEED.

18:52.332 --> 18:53.766
- I KNOW WHAT YOU MEAN.

18:53.800 --> 18:55.668
BUT THEN SOMETHING ALWAYS
HAPPENS TO REMIND ME.

18:55.702 --> 18:58.238
A TOUCH OF THE FLU,
SOMEONE DONATING SPERM,

18:58.271 --> 19:00.307
A LOVER WHO DIES...
- VIC...

19:00.340 --> 19:02.175
