19:45.885 --> 19:49.822
- FUCK.
[knocks on door]

19:49.856 --> 19:52.425
- WHERE'D WE MEET?

19:52.459 --> 19:54.561
UNIFORM NIGHT AT BABYLON?

19:54.594 --> 19:56.829
