BROUGHT YOUR, UH...

19:56.863 --> 19:59.766
HANDCUFFS
AND YOUR NIGHTSTICK.

19:59.799 --> 20:02.602
- I'M OFFICER HANDLEY,
PITTSBURGH POLICE.

20:02.635 --> 20:06.439
- CHRIST. HUH.
YOU'RE FOR REAL.

20:06.473 --> 20:07.974
JESUS.

20:08.007 --> 20:10.410
- YOU NEED TO COME WITH ME
TO HEADQUARTERS, MR. KINNEY.

20:14.747 --> 20:16.383
- NOW YOU'RE SURE YOU WANT
TO DO THIS?

20:16.416 --> 20:17.784
- THANKS.
- BEN AND I WERE UP TALKING

20:17.817 --> 20:19.586
ABOUT IT HALF THE NIGHT.

20:19.619 --> 20:21.621
I THINK HE'S ALMOST AS EXCITED
ABOUT IT AS I AM.

20:21.654 --> 20:24.624
- AND YOU UNDERSTAND
WHAT'S REQUIRED?

20:24.657 --> 20:26.893
- YEAH, UNLESS THEY'RE MAKING
BABIES A NEW WAY THESE DAYS,

20:26.926 --> 20:29.329
I HAVE A PRETTY GOOD IDEA.

20:29.362 --> 20:32.732
- OKAY, THEN ALL YOU
HAVE TO DO IS SIGN THIS.

20:32.765 --> 20:35.868
- "THE DONOR AGREES...

20:35.902 --> 20:38.638
"NO PARENTAL RIGHTS...

20:38.671 --> 20:40.473
VISITATION STRICTLY
BY PERMISSION."

20:40.507 --> 20:41.541
WHAT'S ALL THIS?

20:41.574 --> 20:42.775
- IT'S JUST A FORMALITY.

20:42.809 --> 20:44.477
- FOR YOUR PROTECTION
AS WELL AS OURS.

20:44.511 --> 20:46.513
- PROTECTION FROM WHAT?

20:46.546 --> 20:47.914
- AS YOU CAN SEE...

20:47.947 --> 20:51.351
SECTION TWO,
PARAGRAPH FOUR,

20:51.384 --> 20:53.653
IT RELIEVES YOU OF ANY
FINANCIAL RESPONSIBILITIES

20:53.686 --> 20:54.954
WHATSOEVER.

20:54.987 --> 20:56.623
- "ONCE THE PARTY
OF THE SECOND PART

20:56.656 --> 20:58.057
"HAS PERFORMED HIS FUNCTION,

20:58.090 --> 21:00.627
"HE IS FREE
OF ANY FURTHER OBLIGA--

21:00.660 --> 21:03.496
OBLIGATION."

21:03.530 --> 21:04.831
THAT IS A RELIEF,
KNOWING THAT I'LL NEVER HAVE

21:04.864 --> 21:06.499
TO SEE MY OWN KID.

21:06.533 --> 21:07.767
- WELL, YOU'LL KNOW THE BABY,
MICHAEL,

21:07.800 --> 21:09.369
AND THE BABY
WILL KNOW YOU.

21:09.402 --> 21:10.770
- WELL, SURE, WHEN HE OR SHE
IS OLD ENOUGH,

21:10.803 --> 21:12.772
