THAT I'M "THE DONOR."

21:12.805 --> 21:14.941
- THAT IS WHAT THIS IS ABOUT.

21:14.974 --> 21:17.444
- I MUST HAVE HEARD YOU WRONG,
BECAUSE I SWEAR YOU SAID

21:17.477 --> 21:20.447
YOU WANTED ME
TO BE THE FATHER.

21:23.816 --> 21:25.518
- AFTER WHAT HAPPENED
WITH BRIAN

21:25.552 --> 21:26.919
NOT WANTING TO GIVE UP
HIS PARENTAL RIGHTS,

21:26.953 --> 21:28.821
I'M SURE YOU UNDERSTAND.

21:28.855 --> 21:33.693
- YEAH, AND I'M BEGINNING TO
UNDERSTAND HOW HE MUST'VE FELT.

21:33.726 --> 21:35.395
AND I SURE AS HELL
UNDERSTAND

21:35.428 --> 21:37.964
HOW A KID FEELS
WHO DOESN'T HAVE A DAD,

21:37.997 --> 21:39.466
'CAUSE I DIDN'T HAVE ONE.

21:39.499 --> 21:41.601
SO IF YOU NEED TO DO THIS,
YOU KNOW,

21:41.634 --> 21:43.970
MAKE EVERYTHING LEGAL AND ALL,
THEN GO AHEAD.

21:44.003 --> 21:45.838
I MEAN...

21:45.872 --> 21:49.542
YOU HAVE TO DO
WHAT'S RIGHT FOR YOU, BUT...

21:49.576 --> 21:51.578
SO DO I.

21:54.481 --> 21:55.682
- UHH.

21:55.715 --> 21:58.485
