22:11.531 --> 22:13.633
I KNOW ETHAN'S JEWISH,

22:13.666 --> 22:16.736
SO JUST TELL HIM TO IGNORE
JESUS ON THE CROSS.

22:16.769 --> 22:20.573
AND THIS IS MY FAVE.

22:20.607 --> 22:22.709
IT'S BEEN IN VIC'S ROOM
ALL THESE YEARS.

22:22.742 --> 22:24.444
- BUT I'M WILLING
TO PART WITH IT.

22:24.477 --> 22:26.012
- IT'S TO REMIND YOU THAT,
WHEREVER YOU ARE,

22:26.045 --> 22:29.449
