FOR YOU.

22:29.482 --> 22:32.585
- ARE YOU SURE
YOU DON'T WANT THEM?

22:32.619 --> 22:35.021
- WELL, THEY'RE--THEY'RE
FAMILY HEIRLOOMS, BUT,

22:35.054 --> 22:36.656
