NEED THINGS,

22:36.689 --> 22:39.125
SO I'M PASSING THEM ON
TO YOU AND ETHAN

22:39.158 --> 22:41.628
FOR SAFEKEEPING.

22:46.633 --> 22:49.168
- HI, VIC.
- DETECTIVE HORVATH.

22:49.201 --> 22:52.939
