THAT DIFFERENT FROM US.

23:01.748 --> 23:02.782
- I THOUGHT WE WERE ON
TOMORROW NIGHT.

23:02.815 --> 23:04.484
- WE ARE.

23:04.517 --> 23:07.487
BUT THERE'S SOMETHING I THOUGHT
YOU SHOULD KNOW.

23:07.520 --> 23:10.790
ONE OF YOUR LOST BOYS
IS IN TROUBLE.

23:10.823 --> 23:13.192
- WHICH ONE?
- KINNEY.

23:13.225 --> 23:14.193
- BRIAN?

23:14.226 --> 23:16.095
