OF MOLESTING HIM.

23:22.001 --> 23:23.670
- HOLY SHIT.
- THAT'S BULLSHIT.

23:23.703 --> 23:25.638
THERE'S NO WAY BRIAN
WOULD EVER DO

23:25.672 --> 23:27.674
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.
- HAS HE BEEN ARRESTED?

23:27.707 --> 23:29.576
- SO FAR THEY'RE
JUST QUESTIONING HIM.

23:29.609 --> 23:31.444
- BRIAN MAY BE
A LOT OF THINGS,

23:31.478 --> 23:33.045
AND I'M THE FIRST ONE
TO SAY SO,

23:33.079 --> 23:36.649
BUT HE IS NO CHILD MOLESTER.

23:36.683 --> 23:38.084
