DEEP-FAT-FRY A HORSE APPLE,

24:29.802 --> 24:31.638
AND THEY'D COME RUNNING.

24:31.671 --> 24:35.775
- [chuckles]

24:35.808 --> 24:37.844
AH, WELL, I GUESS
I'M JUST GOING TO GO

24:37.877 --> 24:41.581
WASH MY HANDS.

24:41.614 --> 24:44.517
- OH, BY THE WAY, I HUNG
A FEW THINGS UP IN THERE TO DRY.

24:48.020 --> 24:49.922
- I SEE.

24:49.956 --> 24:52.024
- WHY DON'T YOU SIT DOWN
AND PUT YOUR FEET UP, HONEY?

24:52.058 --> 24:54.293
DIN-DIN BE READY
IN A MIN-MIN!

24:54.326 --> 24:59.031
- RIGHT.

24:59.065 --> 25:01.634
- WHAT--WHAT HAPPENED
TO THE LIVING ROOM?

25:01.668 --> 25:05.171
- OH, I-I FENG SHUI-ED IT.

25:05.204 --> 25:08.541
DO YOU LIKE IT?

25:08.575 --> 25:11.911
- WELL, IT REALLY
GIVES THE ROOM A FLOW.

25:27.994 --> 25:30.797
UH, MY NAIL.

25:30.830 --> 25:32.031
- WHAT, TEDDY?

25:32.064 --> 25:34.667
- THERE WAS A BENT NAIL
RIGHT THERE.

25:34.701 --> 25:37.303
- WHAT,
THAT RUSTY, OLD THING?

25:37.336 --> 25:39.972
- YEAH, YEAH, THAT RUSTY,
OLD THING, WHERE IS IT?

25:40.006 --> 25:42.842
- WELL,
WHILE I WAS FENG SHUI-ING,

25:42.875 --> 25:44.110
