25:44.143 --> 25:45.678
YOU KNOW HOW DANGEROUS
THAT WOULD BE

25:45.712 --> 25:47.079
IF YOU STEPPED ON THAT
IN YOUR BARE FEET?

25:47.113 --> 25:48.347
YOU'D NEED A TETANUS SHOT.

25:48.380 --> 25:49.982
- YEAH, WHAT DID YOU
DO WITH IT?

25:50.016 --> 25:54.053
- I THREW IT OUT.

25:54.086 --> 25:55.988
IT'S JUST AN OLD NAIL.

25:56.022 --> 25:57.824
- IT'S NOT JUST AN OLD NAIL.

25:57.857 --> 26:00.860
IT'S PAVAROTTI'S OLD NAIL.

26:00.893 --> 26:02.328
BEFORE EVERY PERFORMANCE,

26:02.361 --> 26:03.663
HE HAS TO FIND A BENT NAIL
BACKSTAGE FOR GOOD LUCK.

26:03.696 --> 26:05.064
EVERYBODY KNOWS THAT.

26:05.097 --> 26:07.066
THE NIGHT HE WAS IN TOWN
PERFORMING TURANDOT

26:07.099 --> 26:09.268
