HE FOUND THAT NAIL,

26:09.301 --> 26:11.704
PICKED IT UP, KISSED IT,
THREW IT OVER HIS SHOULDER,

26:11.738 --> 26:13.205
AND I PICKED IT UP.

26:13.239 --> 26:15.007
IT'S BEEN MY GOOD LUCK CHARM
EVER SINCE.

26:15.041 --> 26:18.678
NOW IT'S JUST GONE?

26:18.711 --> 26:20.847
- I DIDN'T KNOW.

26:20.880 --> 26:22.381
[music clicks off]

26:22.414 --> 26:23.883
I'M SORRY.

26:23.916 --> 26:25.818
- WELL, YOU HAD NO RIGHT
TOUCHING IT.

26:25.852 --> 26:27.353
YOU HAD NO RIGHT
TOUCHING ANYTHING!

26:27.386 --> 26:28.821
YOU KNOW, I WOULD APPRECIATE
IT IF YOU JUST PUT

26:28.855 --> 26:30.289
EVERYTHING BACK
THE WAY YOU FOUND IT,

26:30.322 --> 26:31.824
AND THAT INCLUDES REMOVING

26:31.858 --> 26:33.626
YOUR DRIPPING SHORTS
FROM MY BATHROOM.

26:33.660 --> 26:36.395
- YOUR BATHROOM?

26:36.428 --> 26:40.099
I'M SORRY, I THOUGHT
IT WAS OUR BATHROOM.

26:40.132 --> 26:44.971
IN FACT, I THOUGHT
THIS WAS OUR PLACE.

26:45.004 --> 26:50.276
APPARENTLY NOT.

26:50.309 --> 26:55.181
WELL, LIKE YOU SAID, HAVE
TO FIND OUT SOONER OR LATER

26:55.214 --> 26:58.417
WHETHER OR NOT
WE COULD LIVE TOGETHER.

26:58.450 --> 27:00.653
BETTER TO HAVE FOUND OUT
SOONER.

27:03.890 --> 27:05.391
[door shuts]

27:05.424 --> 27:08.127
- HE TOLD THEM
YOU MADE HIM SUCK YOUR COCK?

27:08.160 --> 27:10.997
- THAT'S WHAT HE TOLD
MY CUNT-SISTER.

27:11.030 --> 27:12.765
THAT'S WHAT MY CUNT-SISTER
TOLD THE COPS.

27:12.799 --> 27:14.934
- I GAVE THAT LITTLE ASSHOLE
FREE COMICS.

27:14.967 --> 27:17.136
