DO THEY?

27:17.169 --> 27:19.271
- LISTEN UP, MICHAEL.
ARE YOU LISTENING?

27:19.305 --> 27:21.140
- I'M LISTENING.
- THEY'RE HETEROSEXUALS.

27:21.173 --> 27:23.409
THEY THINK ALL US PERVERTS
ARE AFTER ONLY ONE THING:

27:23.442 --> 27:27.146
TO GET OUR HANDS ON SOME
SWEET PIECE OF LITTLE BOY MEAT.

27:27.179 --> 27:28.447
- SO ALL HE HAS TO DO
IS ACCUSE YOU,

27:28.480 --> 27:30.016
AND THEY AUTOMATICALLY
BELIEVE HIM?

27:30.049 --> 27:31.350
- I DUNNO, BUT NOW I HAVE
TO USE THE MONEY

27:31.383 --> 27:33.019
I WAS GOING TO SPEND
ON MY BOTOX TREATMENTS

27:33.052 --> 27:35.922
ON SOME GODDAMN
$300-AN-HOUR LAWYER.

27:35.955 --> 27:37.924
- THEY'RE NOT GOING
TO ARREST YOU, ARE THEY?

27:37.957 --> 27:39.926
- HOW DO I KNOW?
GIVE ME...

27:39.959 --> 27:43.195
- SHIT, YOU COULD GO TO PRISON!
[keys jingling]

27:43.229 --> 27:45.197
- DON'T GET YOURSELF
ALL WORKED UP.

27:45.231 --> 27:46.465
- I'M HALF ITALIAN
AND HALF DRAG-QUEEN.

27:46.498 --> 27:48.167
I'M ALLOWED
TO GET WORKED UP.

27:48.200 --> 27:50.236
WELL,
YOU CAN'T JUST WAIT AROUND

27:50.269 --> 27:53.940
FOR THEM TO COME
AND TAKE YOU AWAY.

27:53.973 --> 27:57.910
- I DON'T INTEND TO.
[tires squealing]

27:57.944 --> 28:00.880
[doorbell rings]

28:04.984 --> 28:07.053
- OH, SHIT.
- OPEN THE DOOR.

28:07.086 --> 28:08.921
- GO AWAY OR I'LL CALL
THE POLICE, YOU SON OF A BITCH.

28:08.955 --> 28:12.792
- I SAID
OPEN THE FUCKING DOOR!

28:12.825 --> 28:16.228
WHERE IS HE?
- GET OUT OF HERE, BRIAN!

28:16.262 --> 28:19.265
- [laughs]

28:19.298 --> 28:20.466
JOHN!

28:20.499 --> 28:22.735
GET YOUR ASS DOWN HERE,
YOU LITTLE FUCK.

28:22.769 --> 28:23.936
- WHAT, YOU THINK
I'M GOING TO LET YOU

28:23.970 --> 28:25.938
GO NEAR HIM,
YOU SICK PERVERT?

28:25.972 --> 28:28.207
[sirens wailing]

28:28.240 --> 28:32.511
- YOU THINK I ACTUALLY
MOLESTED YOUR SON?

28:32.544 --> 28:35.748
YOU KNOW,
MAYBE IF YOU HAD ASKED ME

28:35.782 --> 28:38.017
BEFORE YOU CALLED THE COPS...
- WHY SHOULD I?

28:38.050 --> 28:39.819
AND WHY WOULD HE MAKE IT UP?

28:39.852 --> 28:42.955
- BECAUSE YOUR KID IS A TWISTED,
FAG-HATING LIAR, CLAIRE.

28:42.989 --> 28:48.527
THAT'S WHY.
WHO'D HE LEARN THAT FROM?

28:48.560 --> 28:49.862
OH.

28:49.896 --> 28:51.964
ENTER MOM, STAGE LEFT.

28:51.998 --> 28:54.967
- YOU HAVE A HELL OF A NERVE,
SHOWING YOUR FACE.

28:55.001 --> 28:56.836
- AH.
NICE TO SEE YOU TOO.

28:56.869 --> 28:58.270
WHAT?
DON'T I GET A KISS?

28:58.304 --> 29:00.306
- STAY AWAY FROM ME.
- DON'T WORRY.

29:00.339 --> 29:02.041
YOU'RE NOT MY TYPE.
- GOD ONLY KNOWS

29:02.074 --> 29:03.509
WHAT PERMANENT DAMAGE
YOU'VE DONE TO HIM.

29:03.542 --> 29:05.044
- WHAT?
THAT YOU HAVEN'T DONE ALREADY?

29:05.077 --> 29:06.278
- YOU OUGHT TO BE LOCKED UP.
PUT AWAY.

29:06.312 --> 29:08.848
- THANKS, OLD SPORT.
[glass clinks]

29:08.881 --> 29:10.382
HAVE ANOTHER.

29:10.416 --> 29:12.451
- AND IF I HAVE ANYTHING
TO SAY ABOUT IT, YOU WILL BE.

29:12.484 --> 29:15.521
- HOW COULD YOU?
- HOW COULD I WHAT?

29:15.554 --> 29:20.126
MAKE LITTLE JOHNNY
SUCK MY DICK?

29:20.159 --> 29:23.262
I'M GOING TO FIND YOU,
YOU LITTLE SACK OF SHIT!

29:23.295 --> 29:25.898
AND THIS TIME, YOU WON'T BE
COMING UP FOR AIR!

29:25.932 --> 29:27.166
- DID YOU HEAR THAT,
MOTHER?

29:27.199 --> 29:29.035
HE JUST THREATENED HIM!

29:29.068 --> 29:30.036
I'M CALLING THE POLICE.

29:30.069 --> 29:31.270
- GO AHEAD, SIS.

29:31.303 --> 29:34.540
TELL 'EM
I'M A DEPRAVED MONSTER.

29:34.573 --> 29:36.442
A GODLESS FAG, RIGHT, MOM?

29:36.475 --> 29:37.877
- IF YOU THINK
YOU'RE GETTING A REACTION

29:37.910 --> 29:39.545
FROM ME, YOU'RE NOT.

29:39.578 --> 29:43.449
HOWEVER, I WILL SAY, KNOWING
THE KIND OF LIFE YOU LIVE,

29:43.482 --> 29:47.286
THE TYPE OF PEOPLE
YOU ASSOCIATE WITH,

29:47.319 --> 29:50.056
I'M NOT SURPRISED.

29:50.089 --> 29:55.427
IT'S WHAT HAPPENS WHEN YOU
TURN YOUR BACK ON THE LORD.

29:55.461 --> 29:58.330
- FUCK THE LORD.

30:02.334 --> 30:05.972
AND FUCK YOU.

30:17.884 --> 30:20.386
- I TOLD MY MOM
NOT TO GET HER HOPES UP,

30:20.419 --> 30:23.956
AND THEN SHE HAS TO GO
AND TELL EVERYBODY.

30:23.990 --> 30:25.925
NOW SHE'LL PROBABLY BE
ALL DISAPPOINTED

30:25.958 --> 30:28.360
AND MOPE AROUND FOR DAYS.

30:30.997 --> 30:33.332
- GOOD THING
YOU'RE NOT LIKE HER.

30:33.365 --> 30:36.068
- YEAH.

30:36.102 --> 30:37.937
- [chuckles]

30:37.970 --> 30:40.206
OH, IF IT'S ANY CONSOLATION,

30:40.239 --> 30:41.640
I'M DISAPPOINTED TOO.

30:41.673 --> 30:45.411
I WAS LOOKING FORWARD
TO BEING UNCLE BEN.

30:45.444 --> 30:48.080
- LIKE THE RICE.

30:48.114 --> 30:50.883
- PROBABLY THE CLOSEST
I'LL EVER COME TO BEING A DAD.

30:55.654 --> 30:58.224
- I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU WANTED TO BE ONE.

30:58.257 --> 30:59.391
- IT WAS ALWAYS A THOUGHT,
BUT I NEVER KNEW

30:59.425 --> 31:01.928
HOW MUCH I WANTED IT

31:01.961 --> 31:02.962
UNTIL I COULDN'T.

31:02.995 --> 31:06.098
[door opens]

31:06.132 --> 31:08.534
- SHIT.

31:08.567 --> 31:12.538
THERE'S SOMEBODY
IN THE APARTMENT.

31:12.571 --> 31:18.177
[shuffling]

31:18.210 --> 31:20.446
JESUS, EM.
WHAT'S GOING ON?

31:20.479 --> 31:23.015
WHAT ARE YOU DOING BACK?

31:24.450 --> 31:26.685
- BRIAN WAS RIGHT.

31:26.718 --> 31:30.289
GOOD THING
I SAVED THE BOXES.

31:36.562 --> 31:39.465
[dance music]

31:39.498 --> 31:47.439
*

31:52.211 --> 31:55.681
[laughter]

31:55.714 --> 31:59.285
*

31:59.318 --> 32:04.290
- * DO YOU THINK
YOU CAN RESCUE ME ?

32:04.323 --> 32:07.026
* RESCUE ME,
RESCUE ME *

32:07.059 --> 32:08.227
- HEY, WHERE'S YOUR WIFE?

32:08.260 --> 32:11.163
- SHE WENT HOME TO HER MOTHER.

32:11.197 --> 32:12.698
- LESS THAN 24 HOURS?

32:12.731 --> 32:15.334
WOW, IT SURPASSED
EVEN MY OWN PREDICTIONS.

32:15.367 --> 32:16.735
- CONGRATULATIONS,
YOU MUST FEEL

32:16.768 --> 32:19.205
AN OVERWHELMING SENSE
OF SATISFACTION.

32:19.238 --> 32:20.973
- NAH, WHAT I FEEL IS

32:21.007 --> 32:23.175
AN OVERWHELMING SENSE
OF DISGUST,

32:23.209 --> 32:26.045
SEEING TWO PATHETIC FAGS
TRYING TO TURN THEMSELVES

32:26.078 --> 32:27.479
INTO SOMETHING
EVEN MORE PATHETIC:

32:27.513 --> 32:30.716
TWO HAPPILY MARRIED
HETEROSEXUALS.

32:30.749 --> 32:34.486
- IT'S GOT NOTHING
TO DO WITH THAT.

32:34.520 --> 32:36.255
YOU KNOW, IT'S GOT TO DO
WITH SOMETHING

32:36.288 --> 32:39.525
US LOWER LIFE FORMS
GENERALLY REFER TO AS "LOVE."

32:39.558 --> 32:41.327
JUST BECAUSE YOU
CAN'T COMPREHEND THAT

32:41.360 --> 32:43.195
DOESN'T MEAN THE REST OF US
SHOULD BE CONDEMNED

32:43.229 --> 32:46.498
TO LIVE OUT OUR LIVES
IN SOLITARY CONFINEMENT,

32:46.532 --> 32:50.069
OUR HEARTS BANISHED TO ONE
OF JUPITER'S ICE MOONS.

32:50.102 --> 32:53.272
- WHOA, THAT WAS VERY POETIC

32:53.305 --> 32:55.541
FOR A FORMER ACCOUNTANT.

32:55.574 --> 32:57.276
I SINCERELY HOPE
YOU FIND THE DREAM

32:57.309 --> 32:59.078
THAT SATISFIES
YOUR EXISTENCE.

32:59.111 --> 33:02.281
BUT UNTIL THEN, WHY DON'T YOU
LET ME BUY YOU A DRINK?

33:02.314 --> 33:06.218
- FUCK OFF.

33:06.252 --> 33:07.553
- THAT'S A GOOD IDEA.

33:07.586 --> 33:13.125
*

33:13.159 --> 33:15.094
- YEAH. YEAH.

33:15.127 --> 33:18.664
YEAH.

33:21.567 --> 33:23.535
- HEY.
- HEY.

33:34.680 --> 33:37.449
YOU'RE A LITTLE YOUNG
FOR ME.

33:37.483 --> 33:40.152
- THAT'S NOT WHAT I HEARD.

33:42.488 --> 33:45.424
[arcade hubbub]

34:01.173 --> 34:03.342
- YEAH, MOTHERFUCKERS, DIE.

34:03.375 --> 34:04.743
[gunfire]

34:04.776 --> 34:06.578
- HOW'S CHOIR PRACTICE?

34:06.612 --> 34:09.415
- WHO ARE YOU?
- I'M A FRIEND OF YOUR UNCLE'S.

34:09.448 --> 34:11.417
- ANOTHER FAG?

34:11.450 --> 34:14.153
GET AWAY FROM ME
OR I'LL CALL THE POLICE.

34:14.186 --> 34:16.322
- WHAT ARE YOU
GOING TO TELL 'EM?

34:16.355 --> 34:18.357
THAT I MADE YOU
SUCK ME OFF TOO?

34:18.390 --> 34:20.692
- WHAT DO YOU WANT?
- I WANT THE TRUTH.

34:20.726 --> 34:22.561
- I ALREADY TOLD THE TRUTH.

34:22.594 --> 34:25.097
HE OFFERED ME MONEY,
BUT I WOULDN'T DO IT.

34:25.131 --> 34:26.465
DID HE OFFER YOU MONEY TOO?

34:26.498 --> 34:28.700
- HA.
HE DIDN'T HAVE TO.

34:28.734 --> 34:30.436
I WOULD'VE PAID HIM.

34:30.469 --> 34:32.871
IF YOU DON'T ADMIT
THAT YOU'RE LYING,

34:32.904 --> 34:35.307
THAT YOU MADE ALL OF THIS UP,
BRIAN COULD GO TO JAIL.

34:35.341 --> 34:39.378
- GOOD, THEN HE'D GET RAPED
BY A GANG OF BLACK GUYS.

34:39.411 --> 34:43.449
- YOUR MOTHER
MUST SUBSCRIBE TO HBO.

34:43.482 --> 34:46.718
- WHAT THE FUCK ARE YOU DOING?
GET YOUR HANDS OFF ME!

34:46.752 --> 34:49.621
- THAT'S A COOL BRACELET.

34:53.692 --> 34:56.462
- MAYBE THE TERMS OF
THE AGREEMENT WERE A BIT HARSH.

34:56.495 --> 34:58.464
- I WAS ONLY TRYING
TO PROTECT US.

34:58.497 --> 35:00.199
- BUT MICHAEL'S NOT BRIAN.

35:00.232 --> 35:01.767
THAT'S WHY WE CHOSE HIM
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

35:01.800 --> 35:03.902
- I SAY WE GET A GENIUS
FROM THE SPERM BANK.

35:03.935 --> 35:06.605
IT'S EASIER.
- FOR WHO, MEL? OUR KID?

35:06.638 --> 35:09.208
NEVER KNOWING ITS DAD,
EXCEPT BY A NUMBER?

35:09.241 --> 35:11.810
- I'M NOT HAVING A REPEAT OF
WHAT WE WENT THROUGH WITH BRIAN.

35:11.843 --> 35:14.146
- I JUST SAID
MICHAEL'S NOT BRIAN.

35:14.180 --> 35:15.647
ARE YOU EVEN LISTENING
TO ME?

35:15.681 --> 35:17.883
- BABY, THE ENTIRE STREET'S
LISTENING TO YOU.

35:17.916 --> 35:21.620
- IT'S NOT ABOUT MICHAEL
OR WHO THE FATHER WILL BE.

35:21.653 --> 35:24.356
IT'S ABOUT TRUST--
TRUSTING TO FATE,

35:24.390 --> 35:26.558
TRUSTING TO GOD,

35:26.592 --> 35:29.561
TO THE OB-GYN, THAT SOMEHOW
EVERYTHING WILL BE ALL RIGHT.

35:29.595 --> 35:31.363
NOW, IF YOU CAN'T ACCEPT THAT,

35:31.397 --> 35:33.299
MAYBE YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE
A BABY.

35:33.332 --> 35:35.667
MAYBE WE SHOULD STOP
RIGHT NOW.

35:35.701 --> 35:38.637
- KEEP COMING.
KEEP COMING.

35:38.670 --> 35:40.672
LITTLE MORE.
A LITTLE BIT.

35:40.706 --> 35:44.510
- [sighs]

35:44.543 --> 35:47.513
[CD player playing music]

35:47.546 --> 35:53.419
*

35:53.452 --> 35:57.256
[CD player shuts off]

35:57.289 --> 35:58.390
- WHAT'S UP?

35:58.424 --> 35:59.725
- HOW ABOUT YOU TELLING US?

35:59.758 --> 36:01.527
- LET ME HANDLE THIS,
DEBBIE.

36:01.560 --> 36:03.962
DETECTIVE CARL HORVATH,

36:03.995 --> 36:05.664
PITTSBURGH P.D.

36:05.697 --> 36:07.466
I UNDERSTAND YOU'VE
MADE SOME ALLEGATIONS

36:07.499 --> 36:10.869
RECENTLY REGARDING
YOUR UNCLE, BRIAN KINNEY.

36:10.902 --> 36:13.205
- HE MADE ME DO THINGS TO HIM.

36:13.239 --> 36:15.941
- THAT'S A PRETTY SERIOUS
CHARGE, SON, IF IT'S TRUE.

36:15.974 --> 36:17.543
- I'M NOT LYING.

36:17.576 --> 36:19.545
- HE SAID YOU MADE IT UP
BECAUSE HE FOUND YOU

36:19.578 --> 36:21.280
STEALING MONEY
FROM HIS WALLET.

36:21.313 --> 36:24.216
- HE'S THE LIAR.

36:24.250 --> 36:26.985
- YOU ALSO TOOK SOME KIND
OF BRACELET WITH SHELLS.

36:27.018 --> 36:29.688
- I DON'T HAVE
ANY STUPID BRACELET.

36:29.721 --> 36:31.590
- I SAW YOU WEARING IT TODAY
AT THE ARCADE.

36:31.623 --> 36:33.825
- WHY SHOULD ANYONE
BELIEVE YOU?

36:33.859 --> 36:35.227
- JOHN,
IS THAT THE BRACELET

36:35.261 --> 36:36.828
YOU HAD ON THIS MORNING
AT BREAKFAST?

36:36.862 --> 36:38.330
- MOM, WOULD YOU SHUT UP?

36:38.364 --> 36:39.898
- WELL, YOU SAID YOU GOT IT
AT THE MALL.

36:39.931 --> 36:42.768
- I BOUGHT IT
WITH MY ALLOWANCE

36:42.801 --> 36:45.571
AT THAT STORE
ACROSS FROM THE PET SHOP.

36:45.604 --> 36:47.873
- LET'S SEE THE BRACELET,
SON.

36:47.906 --> 36:49.508
- I DON'T HAVE IT.
I LOST IT.

36:49.541 --> 36:52.911
- [sighs]
SHOW IT TO HIM.

37:07.693 --> 37:10.596
- BRIAN GOT IT IN MEXICO.

37:10.629 --> 37:12.631
HIS INITIALS ARE CARVED
ON ONE OF THE SHELLS.

37:12.664 --> 37:13.999
- MM-HMM.

37:14.032 --> 37:16.668
- I WANT THE TRUTH, JOHN.

37:16.702 --> 37:18.504
NOW YOU TELL ME THE TRUTH.

37:18.537 --> 37:23.675
NOW DID BRIAN REALLY DO
WHAT YOU SAID HE DID?

37:23.709 --> 37:25.511
- HE'S A FAG,
LIKE YOU SAID.

37:25.544 --> 37:28.314
A GODDAMN FAG.

37:29.648 --> 37:32.784
- SHAME ON YOU.

37:39.558 --> 37:43.529
[door shuts]
BUT MOST OF ALL, SHAME ON YOU.

37:48.967 --> 37:50.702
- AND THIS HULK FROM 1988

37:50.736 --> 37:52.671
HAS A REALLY COOL BATTLE
WITH WOLVERINE

37:52.704 --> 37:55.574
AND SOME GREAT ART
BY TODD MACFARLANE.

38:00.879 --> 38:02.348
HI.
- HOPE WE DIDN'T COME

38:02.381 --> 38:03.649
AT A BAD TIME.

38:03.682 --> 38:05.651
- NO, I WAS JUST ADVISING
A COLLECTOR.

38:05.684 --> 38:08.654
HE'S ACTUALLY
ONE OF MY BEST CUSTOMERS.

38:08.687 --> 38:10.456
- THEN WE WON'T STAY
TOO LONG.

38:10.489 --> 38:12.057
MICHAEL,
ABOUT THE AGREEMENT--

38:12.090 --> 38:13.392
- LOOK,
I ALREADY TOLD YOU, I--

38:13.425 --> 38:15.394
- WE KNOW.

38:15.427 --> 38:17.463
THAT'S WHY WE DECIDED
TO AMEND

38:17.496 --> 38:22.434
SOME OF THE FINE POINTS.

38:22.468 --> 38:25.003
- PROVIDED YOU FULFILL
YOUR FUNCTION,

38:25.036 --> 38:29.441
YOU WILL HEREWITH
BE REFERRED TO AS THE FATHER.

38:33.979 --> 38:36.848
- SO WHAT DO YOU SAY, DAD?

38:41.587 --> 38:43.088
[laughter]

38:43.121 --> 38:47.993
- OH!
[laughter]

38:57.503 --> 39:00.606
- MIND IF I HAVE A DRINK?

39:00.639 --> 39:02.974
- NAME ON THE DOOR'S "WOODY'S,"
NOT "EMMETT'S."

39:03.008 --> 39:08.046
- GREY GOOSE AND TONIC.

39:08.079 --> 39:09.848
EM--
- SAVE YOUR BREATH.

39:09.881 --> 39:11.016
IT'S QUITE OBVIOUS
YOU AND I

39:11.049 --> 39:12.584
WERE NOT MEANT
TO LIVE TOGETHER.

39:12.618 --> 39:14.653
- LOOK, I'M SORRY
THAT I GOT UPSET.

39:14.686 --> 39:16.522
- UPSET?
TRY "WENT BALLISTIC."

39:16.555 --> 39:18.457
- JUST,
I'M KIND OF FINICKY...

39:18.490 --> 39:20.726
- FINICKY IS WHEN YOU TURN
YOUR NOSE UP AT FRISKIES.

39:20.759 --> 39:22.728
- WHEN IT COMES
TO MY THINGS.

39:22.761 --> 39:24.463
- AND WHY SHOULDN'T YOU BE,
HONEY?

39:24.496 --> 39:25.864
IT'S YOUR PLACE.

39:25.897 --> 39:27.466
SO, IN THE FUTURE,

39:27.499 --> 39:31.169
DON'T ASK SOMEONE
TO MOVE IN WITH YOU.

39:31.202 --> 39:32.938
- LOOK, AFTER YOU LEFT,

39:32.971 --> 39:35.140
I WALKED UP AND DOWN
LIBERTY AVENUE.

39:35.173 --> 39:36.475
I FINALLY ENDED UP
AT THE DINER

39:36.508 --> 39:37.909
WITH A STALE LEMON BAR

39:37.943 --> 39:39.611
AND A COPY OF LAST WEEK'S
PITTSBURGH OUT.

39:39.645 --> 39:41.079
HAVE YOU SEEN IT?

39:41.112 --> 39:42.881
- IS THE HEADLINE, "FINICKY
BOYFRIEND GOES BERSERK"?

39:42.914 --> 39:44.483
- ACTUALLY, THERE'S
AN INTERESTING LETTER

39:44.516 --> 39:46.752
TO "DEAR ABS"
IN HERE.

39:46.785 --> 39:48.520
- DON'T TELL ME YOU READ
THAT SILLY QUEEN.

39:48.554 --> 39:50.822
- GO ON.

39:55.694 --> 39:58.497
- "DEAR ABS, MY BOYFRIEND
JUST MOVED IN WITH ME,

39:58.530 --> 40:00.899
"AND HE'S TAKEN OVER.

40:00.932 --> 40:04.770
"HE EVEN MOVED THE LUBE
TO THE RIGHT SIDE OF THE BED.

40:04.803 --> 40:09.641
HELP.
ATTA LOSS."

40:09.675 --> 40:12.143
SO?
- NOW HIS ANSWER.

40:14.880 --> 40:17.115
- "DEAR ATTA,

40:17.148 --> 40:20.051
"GET A NEW PLACE
THAT'S BOTH OF YOURS,

40:20.085 --> 40:23.922
"UNLESS YOU WANT
TO JACK OFF ALONE.

40:23.955 --> 40:26.725
"AND AS FOR THE LUBE,
I SUGGEST YOU LET

40:26.758 --> 40:29.461
YOUR BOYFRIEND
PUT IT WHEREVER HE WANTS."

40:32.598 --> 40:34.566
- NOW THERE MUST HAVE BEEN
A REASON I WAS READING THAT

40:34.600 --> 40:36.735
AT 2:00 IN THE MORNING.

40:36.768 --> 40:38.937
I DON'T WANT
TO LOSE YOU, EM,

40:38.970 --> 40:41.540
BUT THERE'S NO WAY WE CAN
LIVE TOGETHER AT MY PLACE.

40:41.573 --> 40:42.841
- YESTERDAY'S NEWS.

40:42.874 --> 40:46.678
- SO I SUGGEST
WE TAKE DEAR ABS' ADVICE

40:46.712 --> 40:48.747
AND GET OUR PLACE--

40:48.780 --> 40:52.083
A SPACE BIG ENOUGH FOR YOU
TO FENG SHUI YOUR HEART OUT

40:52.117 --> 40:55.721
AND FOR ME TO CLOSE THE DOOR
AND TRY AND HIT A HIGH "C"

40:55.754 --> 40:59.024
ALONG WITH PAVAROTTI
IF I WANT TO.

40:59.057 --> 41:04.095
IN FACT,
I WAS THINKING OF A HOUSE.

41:04.129 --> 41:06.097
- A HOUSE?

41:06.131 --> 41:08.834
- WITH A BACKYARD AND ROOMS
FOR YOU TO DECORATE.

41:08.867 --> 41:10.569
- DECORATE?

41:10.602 --> 41:12.838
- IT'S THE BEST INVESTMENT
ONE CAN MAKE.

41:12.871 --> 41:14.239
I MEAN, BESIDES BEING
A GREAT DEDUCTION,

41:14.272 --> 41:16.007
IT'S A PROVEN HEDGE
AGAINST INFLATION

41:16.041 --> 41:18.510
AND AN UNSTABLE ECONOMY.

41:20.278 --> 41:22.714
SO...

41:22.748 --> 41:24.650
WHAT DO YOU SAY?

41:24.683 --> 41:29.621
- I SAY THOSE ARE THE MOST
ROMANTIC WORDS I EVER HEARD.

41:29.655 --> 41:31.823
- YEAH?

41:42.100 --> 41:43.802
- ARE YOU COUNTING OFF
HOW MANY SHOPPING DAYS LEFT

41:43.835 --> 41:45.036
TILL CHRISTMAS?

41:45.070 --> 41:47.939
- IT'S MELANIE'S
OVULATION CYCLE.

41:47.973 --> 41:51.677
- AND WHAT A PERFECT SPOT
FOR IT, RIGHT BESIDE OUR BED.

41:51.710 --> 41:54.880
- WELL, IT'S TO REMIND ME
WHEN WE CAN DO IT

41:54.913 --> 41:56.648
AND WHEN WE CAN'T.

41:56.682 --> 41:58.016
- WHOEVER THOUGHT
OUR SEX LIFE

41:58.049 --> 42:00.619
WOULD BE RULED
BY A FERTILITY CHART?

42:00.652 --> 42:02.020
- WELL, NOW THAT I'M GOING
TO BE A FATHER,

42:02.053 --> 42:03.321
WITH FULL CREDIT
AND EVERYTHING,

42:03.354 --> 42:05.090
I GOTTA BE
EXTRA-SPECIAL RESPONSIBLE.

42:05.123 --> 42:08.159
TONIGHT LOOKS GOOD, THOUGH.
YOU UP FOR IT?

42:08.193 --> 42:09.928
- YEAH, SOON AS I GET BACK
FROM THE GYM.

42:09.961 --> 42:13.164
